thread.title_full: Plastek Cards reviewed by Brian Collins

author: Brian Collins
title: Brian Collins
text: You never know what you're going to get when ordering something from an online vendor for the first time and it can be especially nerve-racking when ordering 1,000's of custom items. Plastek Cards does not disappoint! The print quality was flawless and the card quality is everything I expected... The 12 mil pvc membership cards are thinner than a driver's license, making them easy to slip in your wallet or purse, but they are still very durable â€” much more so than laminated paper cards. We will absolutely be reordering from them and highly recommend them.
